WEBVTT

00:00.126 --> 00:02.423
<i>Previously on
"Once Upon A Time"...</i>

00:02.561 --> 00:03.792
Where's my family?

00:03.797 --> 00:08.154
They're in here now,
in kind of an alternate reality.

00:08.234 --> 00:11.403
So, now we're <i>both</i> trapped
in the book. Congratulations.

00:11.404 --> 00:15.240
I am Rumplestiltskin,
a knight at your service.

00:15.241 --> 00:18.610
The boy I told you about...
he'll be trying to help Regina.

00:18.611 --> 00:20.512
Who are you?
What do you want?

00:20.513 --> 00:22.080
I want you
to kill them both.

00:22.081 --> 00:23.615
Gladly.

00:23.616 --> 00:25.161
Have you ever met someone

00:25.165 --> 00:26.975
that you would change
your entire world for?

00:27.011 --> 00:28.278
Hello, darling.
[ chuckles ]

00:28.279 --> 00:29.840
Regina, I'd like you
to meet my fiancÃ©e.

00:30.024 --> 00:31.609
This is Zelena.

00:31.615 --> 00:34.085
Everything's flipped. This must
be Zelena's happy ending.

00:34.095 --> 00:35.820
We have to stop
this wedding.

00:35.838 --> 00:37.473
There were rumors once
of a woman

00:37.482 --> 00:39.550
<i>who called herself
the savior.</i>

00:39.551 --> 00:41.685
<i>Snow white locked her up
years ago.</i>

00:41.686 --> 00:44.221
<i>The prison she's in
is impenetrable.</i>

00:44.222 --> 00:45.904
[ screaming ]

00:51.463 --> 00:53.523
[ horse whinnies ]

00:57.268 --> 00:59.103
[ horse whinnies ]

00:59.104 --> 01:00.404
Look!

01:00.505 --> 01:02.405
It's him!

01:02.407 --> 01:04.536
[ all shouting excitedly ]

01:07.445 --> 01:08.679
Belle!

01:08.680 --> 01:10.614
[ chuckles ]

01:10.615 --> 01:12.340
[ baby coos ]

01:12.350 --> 01:14.785
Sounds like someone else
wants to celebrate your return.

01:14.786 --> 01:16.227
[ chuckles ]

01:18.756 --> 01:23.660
And how is the newest member
of our dear family?

01:23.661 --> 01:27.498
With any luck, he'll grow up
to be just like dear old dad.

01:27.499 --> 01:30.701
Belle. You didn't tell me
we had a visitor.

01:30.702 --> 01:31.802
Name's Isaac.

01:31.828 --> 01:33.273
I was traveling
through your village,

01:33.285 --> 01:35.487
when your wife invited me in
to slake my thirst.

01:35.507 --> 01:36.536
[ slurps ]

01:37.509 --> 01:38.509
Mm.

01:38.510 --> 01:39.710
Not to be too picky,

01:39.711 --> 01:42.212
but the water
tastes a little murky.

01:42.213 --> 01:45.482
Oh. I'll get some
that's fresh from the well.

01:45.483 --> 01:48.519
[ door opens, closes ]

01:48.520 --> 01:51.622
You didn't come here
for the water.

01:51.623 --> 01:54.224
Perceptive in all worlds.

01:54.225 --> 01:57.161
Good. Yes.

01:57.162 --> 01:59.329
I came here to warn you.

01:59.330 --> 02:01.465
Your happiness
is in danger.

02:01.466 --> 02:02.699
From what?

02:02.700 --> 02:04.401
A boy.

02:04.402 --> 02:06.870
He's on a mission
to help the bandit Regina.

02:06.871 --> 02:10.821
If he succeeds, everything
you have will be destroyed.

02:11.843 --> 02:13.510
Not to mention what <i>I</i> have.

02:13.511 --> 02:15.345
Ha! What nonsense.

02:15.346 --> 02:17.881
How can some stranger's actions
affect my life?

02:17.882 --> 02:21.552
Because your happiness,
your entire life...

02:21.553 --> 02:23.187
It's not real.

02:23.188 --> 02:26.423
I know because I am the one
who created it... with magic.

02:26.424 --> 02:28.659
And it is all
about to crumble.

02:28.660 --> 02:30.928
Regina's true love
is about to marry another.

02:30.929 --> 02:34.565
She's going to try
and stop the wedding.

02:34.566 --> 02:36.351
You cannot let her succeed.

02:37.569 --> 02:38.976
You have to kill her.

02:39.971 --> 02:43.607
Demon! You've been sent here
to try to corrupt me.

02:43.608 --> 02:45.842
You have already
been corrupted.

02:45.843 --> 02:48.545
Before all of this,
you were a villain...

02:48.546 --> 02:50.247
Maybe the worst one of all.

02:50.248 --> 02:52.583
Which is why
you had me use magic

02:52.584 --> 02:54.484
to rewrite your story.

02:54.485 --> 02:55.953
Look,
I can prove it to you.

02:55.954 --> 02:57.955
I-I know things...

02:57.956 --> 03:00.357
the secrets that you've kept
from Belle,

03:00.358 --> 03:04.995
the ones about
your first son... Baelfire.

03:08.533 --> 03:10.667
Where did you hear
that name?

03:10.668 --> 03:14.805
In this story, he was killed
in the ogre wars

03:14.806 --> 03:17.341
despite
your heroic efforts.

03:17.342 --> 03:21.712
But in reality, he died
because of your cowardice.

03:21.713 --> 03:22.879
No, no, no.

03:22.880 --> 03:25.449
I... I protected him.
I did my best.

03:25.450 --> 03:26.857
I...

03:28.920 --> 03:30.554
I was honorable.

03:30.555 --> 03:32.456
No.

03:32.457 --> 03:33.724
You weren't.

03:33.725 --> 03:35.392
He died because of you.

03:35.393 --> 03:36.319
Liar!

03:36.828 --> 03:39.529
Get out of here... <i>now.</i>

03:39.530 --> 03:41.465
All right. I'll go.

03:41.466 --> 03:44.501
But deep down,
you know I'm right.

03:44.502 --> 03:46.603
You're not really a hero.

03:46.604 --> 03:47.938
And if you don't kill Regina

03:47.939 --> 03:49.506
and keep her
from her happy ending,

03:49.507 --> 03:53.595
then everyone, including Belle,
will know, too.

03:58.283 --> 04:01.648
I know you'll make
the right choice, Rumple.

04:01.653 --> 04:03.472
You always do.

04:11.179 --> 04:16.678
<i><font color="#00CCff">Once Upon A Time</font>:
"<font color="#ffd700">Operation Mongoose Part (2/2)</font>"</i>

04:16.685 --> 04:19.885
Season 4 Episode 23
Original Airdate May 10, 2015

04:21.914 --> 04:23.805
Ahoy!

04:26.152 --> 04:27.419
Is anyone here?!

04:27.420 --> 04:29.187
Careful, boy.

04:29.188 --> 04:31.298
No one steps aboard
the <i>Jolly Roger's</i> decks

04:31.310 --> 04:33.708
without an invitation
from its captain first.

04:33.718 --> 04:36.086
Are you gonna make me
walk the plank?

04:36.087 --> 04:37.921
All depends
on why you're here.

04:38.022 --> 04:40.790
I need a ship to take me
to the bottomless sea.

04:40.791 --> 04:43.527
Now, those are
treacherous waters.

04:43.528 --> 04:45.453
There must be something
of great value there

04:45.463 --> 04:46.930
to be worth
taking the risk.

04:46.931 --> 04:48.465
"Someone."

04:48.466 --> 04:50.834
Her name is Emma.
She's my mom.

04:50.835 --> 04:52.903
And she was put there
by the queen.

04:52.904 --> 04:55.739
Well, then,
I'm sorry for you.

04:55.740 --> 04:57.731
Even if I wanted to,
I can't help you.

04:58.943 --> 05:00.944
Why?
You're a captain.

05:00.945 --> 05:03.380
Can't you take your ship
wherever you want?

05:03.381 --> 05:04.748
[ laughs ]

05:04.749 --> 05:06.883
A captain?

05:06.884 --> 05:08.952
Is that who he says he is?

05:08.953 --> 05:10.853
I thought I told you

05:10.854 --> 05:12.756
to be done swabbing the decks
when I return.

05:12.757 --> 05:14.825
I'm sorry,
captain Black Beard.

05:14.826 --> 05:16.360
Wait...
<i>he's</i> the captain?

05:16.361 --> 05:17.661
Indeed.

05:17.662 --> 05:21.062
Unless deckhand Hook
wants to keep playing pretend.

05:22.533 --> 05:24.668
What do you say, Hook?

05:24.669 --> 05:27.971
Beat me,
and the <i>Jolly Roger</i> is yours.

05:27.972 --> 05:32.025
Or are you still
a one-handed coward?

05:33.711 --> 05:35.866
What are you doing?!
Stand up to him!

05:35.895 --> 05:37.150
You <i>can</i> beat him.

05:37.160 --> 05:38.685
I'm afraid
you don't know me very well.

05:38.700 --> 05:40.467
I'm sorry.
I can't help you.

05:40.618 --> 05:42.059
[ scrubbing ]

05:43.020 --> 05:45.046
Then <i>I'll</i> have to help <i>you.</i>

05:45.957 --> 05:47.020
Ugh!

05:48.926 --> 05:50.360
What the bloody hell
are you doing?!

05:50.361 --> 05:52.396
Getting you your ship back.

05:52.397 --> 05:54.398
Come on.
Let's dump Black Beard and go.

05:54.599 --> 05:55.664
You think it's that easy?

05:55.672 --> 05:57.297
I can't sail
the <i>Jolly Roger</i> alone.

05:57.301 --> 05:58.251
I can help.

05:58.252 --> 05:59.703
How do you know
how to sail a ship?

05:59.704 --> 06:03.035
I had a great teacher...
you.

